# Arkiology Website ‚Äî Project Conventions

## Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 16 (App Router, React 19)
- **Language:** TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first `@theme inline`) + CVA + `cn()`
- **Animations:** GSAP 3 + ScrollTrigger, Framer Motion 12, Lenis
- **3D:** Three.js + React Three Fiber + Drei
- **Icons:** Lucide React
- **Email:** Resend (contact form API)
- **Fonts:** Space Grotesk (self-hosted via `next/font/google`)

